Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is actually here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you really managed{/did} it, Taruruuto!{I hope it's dekashita or "succeeded"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what's gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a weird child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come on, let's go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please. My place is a little unkempt,{sounds rather like kogitamae, but has to be kogitanai - a little dirty/messy} \Nbut you're always welcome here.{/thought I know it's a little messy, don't hesitate}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{You should }Be careful when climbing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is coming to my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto's magic is a real deal, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.{/pardon the intrusion}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can explain...{rather it's "I wonder what it is" implying "I was framed, tis is not mine" but I think mine better fits the context and is less cps-heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have guessed you were so corrupt!{/honmaru is a depraved/filthy/lewd person after all}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! Thanks to your perverted potato stamp, \NIyona-chan was so mad she just ran out!{/because of your imoban's fault, livid, yona suddenly went home}
Comment: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato stamp not to blame.{/not my imoban's fault}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru being pervert to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Honmaru had perverted things in mind,\Nthat my potato stamp ended up perverted.{/if you hadn't thought lewds, my stamp would have not been lewd as well}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be true as well.{/I guess that's so}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also the one who asked you \Nto stop the time in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Taruruuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose heart, Honmaru. \NNot all is lost yet.{/It's not too late}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:20:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. But we've had enough of magic.\NI'll {try to }come up with something on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused this mess myself, \NI must fix it myself, somehow.{/figure something out/I reap what I sow, and this time I sew a big mess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no need for listening to excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not excuses! You see, there's a funny story\N about that potato stamp. The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart - Taruruuto made me "Wah, you scared \Nthe life out of me!" - heart jumped out, so he cut it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How low of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to shift the blame onto Taru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are!{/found them, found them}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is even wrong with you? \NImprinting your room with so many indecent...{rather, she says something like "so many [angai/annai/in that state/such pictures] of me" but we only see one here, so I guess smt like "Photographing me in such an unseemly state!" allows for a better flow, and the current opion sits better with the next line, even though omits watashi and conjures "stamping your room"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pictures of Taru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what exactly \NI'd been so mad about a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, but what about the potato stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The potato stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun! I'm so sorry \Nfor being that rude,{/for doing that terrible/cruel thing} Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With magic, I rewrote{/erased} Iyona's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, for friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you spare no magic.{I go with assuming this is omoke - discount/bonus, implying "we're friends so you get an extra magic from me/so I'm not stingy with magic for you" but may be omoki and accordingly "friends are the essence of magic/are important for magic/are the emphasized with magic" or even something completely different} {yume: Not 100% sure, most likely "魔法の円に--" -> From context: "Honmaru, we're friends." into "Here's a magical circle to help you."}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make the pain go away sooner.{/this way, it will hurt a little less}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so caring, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, can I ask you just one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, in the girls' changing room, \Nwhy did you touch me like that?{rather, she asks "why did you do that in the girls locker room" but this sounds not expressive enough and I'm not that conscienceless to invent "why did you try to pull down my bra strap"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember things from that time?{/you remember it clearly? - methinks he implies 'I thought you were still frozen' but may be just 'I thought you have forgotten already'}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get it out of my mind.{/it is worrying me/It seared into my memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a love letter and...{/I wanted [to give you] a love letter}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
