Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru?
Comment: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing to my Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A very arrogant heir to a nuclear power corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako Tsutomu{upd: it's a game of words: 原子力 (atomic energy/nuclear power) together is genshinryoku, but if you read each kanji as kunyomi, it goes "hara ko tsutomu" and literally means "elementary matter child's effort" or, if you twist your brain really hard, it's something like "empowered with atoms" or "son of the primitive power" and that's the way the guy is introduced to us for the first time}, has taken Iyona-chan out for a drive against her will!
